- `game/src/ui/researchPanel.js` — added _ageSection() rendering current age info + next age requirements checklist + Advance button; subscribes to AGE_CHANGED, BUILDING_CHANGED, UNIT_CHANGED for live requirement updates; onclick wired to advanceAge()
- `game/src/main.js` — imported AGES and on; added _updateAgeBadge() on boot and AGE_CHANGED; saves/loads age in save state (version 3); emits AGE_CHANGED on new game reset
