**Architecture decisions:**
- Age productionMult is cumulative per age (Stone=1.0, Bronze=1.25, Iron=1.5, Medieval=2.0) — not stacking per age step
- Age mult applied ONLY to building production (not baseline income, territory bonuses, or consumption) for clean separation
- Requirements are checked at click time (no pre-check flag), keeping state minimal
- Age badge in title bar provides ambient awareness without cluttering gameplay panels
- Research panel is the natural home for age advancement (progression/research theme)

